DescDetail: <<
Symbolic toolbox based on GiNaC and CLN.
The package provides the following functions:
Symbols:
        symbols
        sym
        ex_matrix
        Pi
Extended precision arithmetic:
        digits
        vpa
        to_double
Properties:
        is_ex
        is_ex_matrix
        is_sym
        is_vpa
        syminfo
Expression manipulation:
        subs
        collect
        expand
        lcoeff
        numden
        findsymbols
        findsym
Special Functions:
        Abs
        Cos
        Cosh
        Exp
        Gcd
        Log
        Sin
        Sinh
        Tan
        Tanh
        aCos
        aCosh
        aSin
        aSinh
        aTan
        aTanh
        Sqrt
Polynomials:
        tcoeff
        coeff
        degree
        ldegree
        sym2poly
        poly2sym
        sumterms
Calculus
        differentiate
Solving Equations:
        symlsolve
        symfsolve
Number theory:
        probably_prime
        quotient
        remainder
        premainder
Plot:
        splot
Conversion:
        to_char

<<
